---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Opportunities | Dr. Toby Brown"
  description="Graduate student and postdoctoral opportunities with Dr. Toby Brown at Herzberg and the University of Victoria. Plaskett, Covington, Instrument Science, and NRC fellowships."
>
  <div class="opportunities">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Opportunities</h1>
      <p class="lead">Prospective students and postdocs</p>

      <figure class="hero-image">
        <img src="/images/haa.jpg" alt="Herzberg Astronomy and Astrophysics Research Centre" width="600" height="340" loading="eager" />
        <figcaption>Herzberg Astronomy and Astrophysics Research Centre</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <div class="facilities">
        <span class="facility">SKA</span>
        <span class="facility">VLT/MUSE</span>
        <span class="facility">ALMA</span>
        <span class="facility">CANFAR</span>
        <span class="facility">HST</span>
        <span class="facility">LOFAR</span>
        <span class="facility">MeerKAT</span>
        <span class="facility">Rubin</span>
      </div>

      <p class="intro">
        At the Herzberg Astronomy and Astrophysics Research Centre, we conduct world-class research across a broad range of astrophysics. We have access to current and future premier facilities like SKA, CHORD, ALMA, Rubin Observatory, Gemini Observatory, Canada France Hawaii Telescope, and state-of-the-art labs. I am also part of the Canadian Astronomy Data Centre at Herzberg which provides world-leading data services and cloud computing.
      </p>

      <div class="opportunities-grid">
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Graduate Students</h2>
          <p>My research regularly generates opportunities and projects for graduate students as well as a chance to collaborate with leading astronomers around the world. If you're a prospective graduate student interested in related research areas, I strongly encourage you to apply to the <a href="https://www.uvic.ca/science/physics/graduate/astronomy/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">University of Victoria's Astronomy program</a>. I hold adjunct status at UVic and regularly supervise and collaborate with UVic students.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Postdoctoral Researchers</h2>
          <p>We offer four regular postdoctoral fellowship programs at Herzberg:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Plaskett Fellowship</li>
            <li>Covington Fellowship</li>
            <li>Instrument Science Fellowship</li>
            <li>NRC annual open postdoctoral program</li>
          </ul>
          <p>For postdoctoral researchers who share the interests above, I'm always open to discussing fellowship proposals, and I recommend considering the postdoctoral positions at Herzberg and NRC.</p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="/contact/">Contact me</a> to discuss opportunitiesâ€”I'd love to hear from you.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .opportunities {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  }
  .opportunities h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .lead {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
  }
  .hero-image {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
  }
  .hero-image img {
    max-width: 480px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .hero-image figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .facilities {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .facility {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    background: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .opportunities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .opportunities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .card {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .card p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .card ul {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
